<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>商业 on 短松江月</title><link>https://simons.qzz.io/categories/%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A/</link><description>Recent content in 商业 on 短松江月</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 29 Jan 2026 11:32:58 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://simons.qzz.io/categories/%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>品牌取名四要</title><link>https://simons.qzz.io/post/2025/04/four_essentials_for_brand_naming/</link><pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 08:44:05 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://simons.qzz.io/post/2025/04/four_essentials_for_brand_naming/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;定位理论的创始人里斯和特劳特非常重视取名，甚至在《定位》中说：“在定位时代，你能做的唯一重要的营销决策就是为你的产品取个好名字。”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://ts1.tc.mm.bing.net/th/id/R-C.eea819ef057e784cfdeb39e2f6f29e2d?rik=gPFB%2bnknDzuYaw&amp;amp;riu=http%3a%2f%2fdingweililun.com%2fueditor%2fphp%2fupload%2fimage%2f20181120%2f1542705073628148.jpg&amp;amp;ehk=rBn7WAp2TgvamaXktHe%2fVe7QX%2fZkFjz1rzNpmvXBwKk%3d&amp;amp;risl=&amp;amp;pid=ImgRaw&amp;amp;r=0" alt="21世纪，“定位之父”艾•里斯如何定位“定位理论”？"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;天图投资的冯卫东说，根据他二十多年的投资经验来看，好名字不一定会成功，但是坏名字一定很难成功。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;好名字能有效进行定位沟通和传播。坏名称难记难写，在顾客心中留下一个印象很不容易。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>实现本土化：可口可乐“摸着石头过河”</title><link>https://simons.qzz.io/post/2025/03/coca-cola_crosses_the_river_by_feeling_the_stones/</link><pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 01:36:28 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://simons.qzz.io/post/2025/03/coca-cola_crosses_the_river_by_feeling_the_stones/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;
